init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He told me that he knew how it felt, and has been through the same experience of living a lifetime of experiences.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: , and has been through the same experience of living a lifetime of experiences.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I sat there thinking about the life I just left behind.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I got up, walked toward the exit of the theater, and discovered that there was no door.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked back at my younger self, and then at the other people sitting in the theater.
